# Project Rules for AI Chat App

## Project Description

Below you will find specifications about this project. Make sure to follow the project convention and Style.

## Project Context

Mobile App using Flutter and Dart. This is a AI Chat App that:

- chat with ai and automate with ai
- help user organize their ai chats

## Testing

- Unit Testing with Mocktail and bloc_test

## Coding Rules

- Create a new file for each widget.
- Use StatelessWidget if possible.
- Keep state as local as possible
- Avoid using Extracting Widgets into Methods, prefer to extract in separate Widgets.
- Use tool `context7` to get documentation if needed
